And then you are kind of picking up the baton and saying like, well, now I need to turn

00:04:51.480 --> 00:04:54.720
that data into useful data sets.

00:04:54.720 --> 00:05:02.040
And I may not even be the consumer of that data set, but I know that there are, you know,

00:05:02.040 --> 00:05:08.359
a handful to dozens to maybe hundreds of consumers of this data set that I will create.

