But it doesn't do other stuff.

00:05:19.359 --> 00:05:21.079
It doesn't build charts or graphs.

00:05:21.079 --> 00:05:22.959
It doesn't move data, this kind of stuff.

00:05:22.959 --> 00:05:27.440
Yeah, I think that's a really interesting perspective because I've always, like the

