sort of the data science model, like the alpha data science model is always like you as the

00:05:31.959 --> 00:05:37.399
data scientist trying to push, like to own as much of the stack as possible.

00:05:37.399 --> 00:05:41.720
Like you, you know, hopefully you can get some of your data from a nice, you know, SQL

00:05:41.720 --> 00:05:45.559
database somewhere, but often you're going to might have to do some scraping or, you

00:05:45.559 --> 00:05:48.519
know, pull together 15 random Excel sheets.

00:05:48.519 --> 00:05:49.959
