science model is, is kind of terrible because the organization may have to do this business

00:08:09.679 --> 00:08:11.799
process for multiple decades.

00:08:11.799 --> 00:08:17.160
And certainly like individual people will come and go over that time period and your

00:08:17.160 --> 00:08:22.480
process needs to be like very standardized and, and, you know, transferable between humans.

00:08:22.480 --> 00:08:23.480
Yes.

00:08:23.480 --> 00:08:29.519
It sounds, yeah, like a much, it's much more like business as usual when almost like the

